  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient harboring a GRE or CRE bacteria

          -  Colonization confirmed by our microbiology department, including at least 3 positives
             swabs in the last month

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant woman or breastfeeding

          -  immunosuppression including AIDS, corticosteroids over 60mg/day

          -  ongoing antibiotic treatment at the day of inclusion

          -  impossibility to obtain a signed consent form.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
